<section class="section" aria-labelledby="roadmap-sections-title">
  <div class="section-heading">
    <div>
      <h2 id="roadmap-sections-title">Current roadmap</h2>
      <p class="section-meta">Last updated: June 18, 2026</p>
    </div>
    <p>Priorities may change as the app evolves. For current Free and Premium feature ownership, use the comparison on the home page.</p>
