  <div class="roadmap-grid">
    <article class="card roadmap-card">
      <div class="roadmap-card-header">
        <h2>Shipped recently</h2>
        <span class="status-badge status-shipped">Shipped</span>
      </div>
      <ul class="roadmap-list">
        <li><strong>Manual batch costing</strong> &mdash; Cost multiple copies, multiple models, or a mix of both in one workflow. Free includes manual batch costing for up to 3 items per batch, with larger-scale batch workflows available in Premium.</li>
        <li><strong>Premium pricing controls</strong> &mdash; Markup, setup fees, and rounding rules for cleaner business pricing when you need to move from cost to charge.</li>
        <li><strong>Single-print G-code import</strong> &mdash; Import supported print data into the calculator faster without typing every detail by hand.</li>
      </ul>
    </article>

    <article class="card roadmap-card">
      <div class="roadmap-card-header">
        <h2>In Progress</h2>
        <span class="status-badge status-in-progress">In Progress</span>
      </div>
      <ul class="roadmap-list">
        <li><strong>Client view with a shareable quote</strong> &mdash; Build on Premium pricing controls with a cleaner quote-style view that can be shared with customers.</li>
        <li><strong>Improved batch export options</strong> &mdash; More ways to share and present batch quote output.</li>
      </ul>
    </article>

    <article class="card roadmap-card">
      <div class="roadmap-card-header">
        <h2>Planned</h2>
        <span class="status-badge status-planned">Planned</span>
      </div>
      <ul class="roadmap-list">
        <li>Backup and restore with JSON files</li>
        <li>More automatic cost filling from supported G-code data after import</li>
        <li>Preset import for faster setup</li>
        <li>Expanded material import options for faster setup</li>
      </ul>
    </article>

    <article class="card roadmap-card">
      <div class="roadmap-card-header">
        <h2>Exploring</h2>
        <span class="status-badge status-exploring">Exploring</span>
      </div>
      <ul class="roadmap-list">
        <li><strong>Expanded help and FAQ content</strong> &mdash; More in-app guidance and troubleshooting resources.</li>
        <li><strong>More guided setup for new users</strong> &mdash; Step-by-step onboarding to help new users get started faster.</li>
      </ul>
    </article>
